</code></pre></div></div>

<h3 id="448-创建所有的hash-table">4.4.8. 创建所有的hash table</h3>
<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1"># Creating the hashtables
</span><span class="n">hash_tables</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
